  <text xml:lang="ta">
    <body>
      <div xml:id="Aink60-kilavi">
        <p type="edition">varaiyātoḻukum talaimakaṉ iravukkuṟi vantuḻit tōḻi colliyatu.
        </p>
        <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
      </div>
      <div xml:id="Aink60">
        <lg type="edition">
          <l>paḻaṉak kampuḷ payirppeṭai yakavuṅ</l>
          <l>kaḻaṉi yūraniṉ moḻiva leṉṟun</l>
          <l>tuñcumaṉai neṭunakar varuti</l>
          <l>yañcā yōviva ṭantaikai vēlē.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


          <l> O man from the village of paddy-fields </l>
          <l rend="indent2"> where the keening hen of the tank-[dwelling] water-fowl calls!</l>
          <l>(OR: where the water-bird in the tank calls out to his keening hen)</l>
          <l> I have something to tell you. </l>
          <l> You are always coming to our large compound when the house is sleeping.</l>
          <l> Are you not afraid of the spear in her father's hand? </l>


        </lg>
      </div>
    </body>
